descriptionHtml:
My chars preset.

Requirements to make it look exactly like in teh pictures:

- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url]
- KS Hairdos [400] (Google It, it's on Tumblr "Ks Hairdo's")
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49963/?]True Eyes[/url] (Optional)
-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/21602/?] Lunari Race [/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Eyebrows[/url] (Optional)
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/48705/?]RaceMenu Overlay Compilation UNP Version[/url] (Optional)
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49414/?]Pubic Hairstyle Overlays for RaceMenu[/url] (Optional)
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6923/?]Extended Slider Colors! [/url](Optional)

Body used in screenshots: UNP with BBP tho you probably don't care anyway.

[b]Installation:[/b] Download archive manualy and extract it then copy "IE33's Kitten.jslot" to your Chargen Preset folder, which should be located in: \Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets

Ur Done..

TL;DR.
Nah, It took me too much tiem to write all this stuff so no TL;DR.
